ON A SCIENCE PROJECT

07:57.377 --> 07:58.979
FOR SCIENCE.

07:59.012 --> 08:01.014
ABOUT VOLCANOES.
AND WIND.

08:01.048 --> 08:03.550
[ HIGH‐PITCHED RINGING ]

08:05.686 --> 08:07.754
