N‐NICE MEETING YOU.

09:23.730 --> 09:25.399
GO, SCIENCE.

09:27.167 --> 09:28.435
WHEN'S SHE LEAVING?

09:28.468 --> 09:29.403
SOON.

09:29.436 --> 09:31.872
