HER LANDMARK FORUM SUMMIT

09:40.013 --> 09:41.181
AT A HOTEL BY THE AIRPORT.

09:41.215 --> 09:43.383
IT'S LIKE A SELF‐IMPROVEMENT
PYRAMID SCHEME.

09:43.417 --> 09:44.551
