NO, THE HEADACHE
IS MERELY A SYMPTOM.

14:30.170 --> 14:36.076
I KNOW A MAN WITH
AN UNCONVENTIONAL MEDICINE.

14:36.109 --> 14:39.046
IT WILL HELP YOU.

14:39.079 --> 14:42.683
AND I'LL TAKE CARE OF YOU
EVERY STEP OF THE WAY.

14:42.716 --> 14:44.218
DO YOU TRUST ME?

14:47.154 --> 14:49.489
DO YOU TRUST ME?

14:54.828 --> 14:56.530
[ SIGHS ]
I TRUST YOU.

14:58.665 --> 14:59.867
GOOD.

14:59.900 --> 15:02.236
GOOD.

15:04.304 --> 15:08.075
"AND YOU HAVE RUINED THE BEST
YEARS OF YOUR LIFE AND MINE.

15:08.108 --> 15:10.043
"YOU CAN'T HAVE
YOUR FAMILY BACK.

15:10.077 --> 15:11.545
"YOU CAN'T HAVE ME BACK.

15:11.578 --> 15:16.083
"BUT THERE IS STILL ONE PERSON
YOU CAN HAVE BACK.

15:16.116 --> 15:17.618
"DO YOU KNOW
WHO THAT PERSON IS?

15:17.651 --> 15:19.753
THAT PERSON IS Y‐‐"

15:19.786 --> 15:21.588
OHH!

15:21.622 --> 15:22.990
AAH!

15:23.023 --> 15:27.628
HOW DARE
ANY OF YOU JUDGE ME!

15:27.661 --> 15:29.129
FUCK!

15:29.162 --> 15:30.163
YOU!

15:30.197 --> 15:32.833
YOU WITH
YOUR LOW‐TESTOSTERONE,

15:32.866 --> 15:35.068
HUMP‐SHOULDERED
VICTIM SHIT!

15:35.102 --> 15:38.405
YOU ARE THE REASON I STARTED
DRINKING IN THE FIRST PLACE!

15:38.438 --> 15:43.076
AND YOU ‐‐ YOU AND YOUR SISTER
SUCKED ME DRY.

15:43.110 --> 15:47.414
WANT, NEED, DEMAND ‐‐
A CONSTANT DRAIN!

15:47.447 --> 15:51.451
WHO COULD RESIST
A LITTLE CAPSULE‐SHAPED ESCAPE?

15:51.485 --> 15:53.086
AND YOU ‐‐ I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHY YOU'RE HERE.

15:53.120 --> 15:54.988
YOU'RE MY BITCH.

15:55.022 --> 15:57.057
I USE YOU, AND YOU'RE TOO STUPID
TO REALIZE IT, SO...

15:57.090 --> 15:58.559
HEY! I REALIZE IT!

15:58.592 --> 15:59.993
BUT I DON'T CARE.

16:00.027 --> 16:03.096
WILL SHE STILL BE FUN
WHEN SHE'S SOBER?

16:03.130 --> 16:04.131
THIS IS POINTLESS.

16:04.164 --> 16:06.133
IT'S YOUR TURN, ISABEL.

16:06.166 --> 16:11.271
GIVE ME...
THE...FUCKING...KEY!

16:17.211 --> 16:19.980
"YOU PUT ME
ON LIQUID DIETS

16:20.013 --> 16:23.851
"AND SNUCK LAXATIVES
INTO MY CHOCOLATE STASH.

16:23.884 --> 16:26.987
"YOU MADE ME DO ULTRA TAE BO
WHEN I WAS 6.

16:27.020 --> 16:31.325
YOU TOLD ME I WOULD NEVER BE
LOVED WHEN I WAS FAT."

16:31.358 --> 16:33.260
WHAT'S YOUR POINT?
"YOU INSTILLED IN ME

16:33.293 --> 16:36.163
"THE SAME THINGS
YOUR MOTHER INSTILLED IN YOU ‐‐

16:36.196 --> 16:41.134
"DEEP ANGER, DISTRUST,
AND SELF‐LOATHING.

16:41.168 --> 16:44.505
"BUT AT LEAST BACK THEN
YOU GAVE A SHIT.

16:44.538 --> 16:47.774
NOW YOU'RE JUST A ZOMBIE."

16:47.808 --> 16:54.314
IF YOU DON'T DEAL WITH THIS,
I WILL CALL YOUR MOTHER.

16:55.549 --> 16:57.484
AH!

17:01.488 --> 17:03.991
[ CHANTING ]

17:04.024 --> 17:06.094
Nancy: IS IT TEA?

17:06.127 --> 17:08.363
IT'S AYAHUASCA.

17:08.396 --> 17:11.699
MADE FROM PLANTS
FROM THE AMAZON RAINFOREST.

17:11.733 --> 17:14.035
KUCHO WILL TAKE CARE OF US.

17:14.068 --> 17:18.139
I DRINK IT
WHEN I NEED HEALING, CLARITY.

17:18.173 --> 17:20.275
I DRINK IT TO LEARN.

17:20.308 --> 17:21.509
IT'S MAGIC.

17:21.543 --> 17:23.611
PEYOTE MAGIC?

17:23.645 --> 17:26.147
LIKE HALLUCINOGENIC MAGIC?

17:26.181 --> 17:30.485
NO, PEYOTE IS A BICYCLE.
AYAHUASCA'S A ROCKET SHIP.

17:30.518 --> 17:33.621
LIKE 30 YEARS OF PSYCHOTHERAPY
IN ONE NIGHT.

17:33.655 --> 17:36.591
BUT I ONLY HAVE
A HEADACHE.

17:36.624 --> 17:40.695
YOU HAVE A TIGHTLY WOUND KNOT
IN YOUR SOUL.

17:40.728 --> 17:42.931
THIS WILL UNWIND IT.

17:42.964 --> 17:45.266
[ KUCHO WHISPERING IN SPANISH ]

18:11.626 --> 18:13.161
[ TWITTERING ]

18:13.194 --> 18:16.197
[ WOMAN CHANTING ]

18:19.734 --> 18:21.202
[ WHISPERING CONTINUES ]

18:25.874 --> 18:28.409
NO. NO, NO.

18:39.053 --> 18:40.321
W‐WHAT'S WRONG?
WHAT DID HE SAY?

18:40.355 --> 18:43.358
N‐NOTHING'S WRONG.
EVERYTHING'S OKAY.

18:43.391 --> 18:45.293
DRINK.

18:45.326 --> 18:47.028
DRINK.

18:47.061 --> 18:49.097
[ TWITTERING ]

18:49.130 --> 18:50.965
[ WHISPERING IN SPANISH ]

18:50.999 --> 18:53.468
GO AHEAD, DRINK.

18:56.437 --> 18:58.072
[ TWITTERING ]

18:58.106 --> 19:00.074
[ WOMAN CHANTING ]

19:03.611 --> 19:07.148
[ WHISPERING CONTINUES ]

19:07.182 --> 19:10.151
[ PSYCHEDELIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

19:23.097 --> 19:26.668
Kucho: [ SINGING IN SPANISH ]

19:50.158 --> 19:52.460
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

20:01.336 --> 20:04.172
YOU KNOW. YOU KNOW. YOU KNOW.

20:05.139 --> 20:07.742
YOU KNOW. YOU KNOW.
YOU KNOW. YOU KNOW.

20:07.775 --> 20:09.811
NO MORE HIDING.

20:09.844 --> 20:11.312
NO MORE HIDING.

20:11.346 --> 20:12.514
NO MORE HIDING.

20:12.547 --> 20:14.282
NO MORE HIDING.

20:16.150 --> 20:18.019
YOU KNOW. YOU KNOW.

20:20.021 --> 20:21.990
NO MORE HIDING.

20:24.659 --> 20:26.027
IT'S OUT.

20:27.962 --> 20:29.564
IT'S OUT.

20:36.004 --> 20:37.605
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

20:41.176 --> 20:45.113
HI.
I AM SO SORRY.

20:45.146 --> 20:47.549
AFTER THE MEDIATION,
HENRY AND I WENT OUT FOR DINNER.

20:47.582 --> 20:48.917
HENRY?

20:48.950 --> 20:51.019
YOU WENT OUT TO EAT
WITH YOUR EX‐HUSBAND?

20:51.052 --> 20:53.221
I'M SITTING HERE BABYSITTING
YOUR INSOMNIAC SON.

20:53.254 --> 20:56.024
SILAS,
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

20:56.057 --> 20:58.059
LIFE GETS
A LITTLE MORE COMPLICATED ‐‐

20:58.092 --> 20:59.494
DID YOU FUCK HIM?

21:03.464 --> 21:04.999
DO YOU WANT THE TRUTH?

21:05.033 --> 21:07.001
YES, I WANT THE TRUTH.

21:07.035 --> 21:09.504
THE TRUTH IS IN 10 YEARS,

21:09.537 --> 21:13.107
I'M GONNA BE ALMOST 50,

21:13.141 --> 21:14.776
AND YOU WON'T EVEN BE 30.

21:14.809 --> 21:19.013
THE TRUTH IS THAT YOU AND I
HAVE A LOT OF FUN RIGHT NOW,

21:19.047 --> 21:23.618
AND NEITHER ONE OF US
WANTS THAT TO END...RIGHT?

21:31.025 --> 21:33.061
DO YOU WANT ME TO GO?

21:39.901 --> 21:41.736
YOU MADE HIM ROTELLI?

21:41.769 --> 21:43.738
PENNE.

21:43.771 --> 21:46.608
AND, NO...

21:46.641 --> 21:49.277
I DON'T WANT YOU TO GO.

22:11.766 --> 22:13.334
NO, I'M GOOD.
I GOT IT COVERED. GO.

22:13.368 --> 22:15.603
YOU SURE?
YEAH, GO, GO, GO.

22:15.637 --> 22:16.938
I'M ON THE JOB.

22:16.971 --> 22:18.973
NEVER FEAR.
DOUG IS HERE.

22:19.007 --> 22:20.808
I'M GONNA GO TROLL THE GYM
FOR SOME STRANGE.

22:20.842 --> 22:22.977
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

22:23.011 --> 22:24.479
AMERICA FIRST.

22:24.512 --> 22:26.314
AMERICA FIRST!

22:29.350 --> 22:30.985
[ Dialing ]

22:31.019 --> 22:34.222
THE CAT'S AWAY.
BRING ME MY BABY.

22:42.096 --> 22:46.034
♪♪ AH, AH, AH ♪♪

22:50.872 --> 22:54.175
♪♪ AH, AH, AH ♪♪

22:56.010 --> 22:57.412
[ LAUGHING ]

22:59.147 --> 23:01.249
YOU'RE AS BEAUTIFUL
AS I REMEMBER.

23:01.282 --> 23:03.785
AND YOU ARE AS TALL
AS I REMEMBER.

23:03.818 --> 23:04.786
[ LAUGHS ]

23:04.819 --> 23:07.055
AND YOU ARE VERY HANDSOME!

23:08.089 --> 23:09.991
ANDY, ANDY,
WHAT'S HE DOING?!

23:10.024 --> 23:12.060
I THINK HE THINKS
IT'S PART OF THE PROTOCOL.

23:12.093 --> 23:13.328
WELL,
TELL HIM TO FUCK OFF.

23:13.361 --> 23:15.363
YEAH, LET'S GO.
LET'S GO.

23:15.396 --> 23:17.799
COME ON. ANDALE!

23:17.832 --> 23:19.534
LOOK AT YOU!

23:19.567 --> 23:22.003
COME ON. COME ON.

23:22.036 --> 23:23.972
YOU'RE GONNA LOVE
THIS COUNTRY ‐‐

23:24.005 --> 23:26.608
THE LAND OF FREEDOM
AND OPPORTUNITY.

23:26.641 --> 23:30.945
AND...AIR‐CONDITIONING.

23:30.979 --> 23:33.481
HUH? YOU LIKE THAT?

23:33.515 --> 23:36.050
THAT'S THE COOL BREEZE
OF FREEDOM RIGHT THERE.

23:51.499 --> 23:52.600
HEY.

23:55.103 --> 23:57.071
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

23:59.674 --> 24:01.609
NO HEADACHES.

24:01.643 --> 24:04.078
NO PAIN EVER AGAIN.

24:04.112 --> 24:07.315
NOT IF I CAN HELP IT.

24:07.348 --> 24:11.452
YOU JUST RELAX NOW,
OKAY?

24:11.486 --> 24:14.923
SOON YOU CAN GET UP
AND TAKE A NICE, LONG BATH.

24:14.956 --> 24:17.859
THERE'S PLENTY OF FOOD FOR US
IN THE KITCHEN.

24:17.892 --> 24:21.129
DID I MAKE
EVERYTHING BETTER?

24:29.871 --> 24:31.406
YOU THINK I'M AN IDIOT,
WILSON?

24:31.439 --> 24:33.975
DOUBLE‐CROSSING,
ANTI‐AMERICAN PIECE OF SHIT!

24:34.008 --> 24:36.377
CORNHOLING YOUR WAY
INTO OUR GOOD GRACES?

24:36.411 --> 24:38.680
YOU GOT THE WRONG IDEA, SCHMIDT.
I'M JUST ROUNDING THEM UP.

24:38.713 --> 24:40.582
ROUNDING THEM UP
WITH HUGS?

24:40.615 --> 24:43.318
LOVE KNOWS NO BORDERS,
MAN.

24:43.351 --> 24:45.220
Come here.

24:45.253 --> 24:47.088
YOU SEE THIS GIRL HERE?

24:47.121 --> 24:49.157
THIS IS THE LOVE
OF HIS LIFE.

24:50.058 --> 24:52.026
SHE'S THE WOMAN
THAT HE'S GONNA MARRY.

24:52.060 --> 24:53.361
WHOA. WHOA.
RUSHING THINGS A BIT, ANDY.

24:53.394 --> 24:54.162
BE COOL.

24:54.195 --> 24:56.030
YOU BREAK MY HEART,
WILSON.

24:56.064 --> 24:59.167
I LET YOU IN,
AND YOU SHIT ON MY FACE.

24:59.200 --> 25:03.137
LOOK, TEX, I BET YOU WOULD RISK
LIFE AND LIMB

25:03.171 --> 25:06.875
FOR YOUR STEROID‐PUMPED
SNOW WHITE.

25:06.908 --> 25:08.843
YOU TOLD HIM ABOUT HOPE?

25:08.877 --> 25:12.013
[ STUTTERS ]

25:12.046 --> 25:14.616
LOOK, PAL, THIS IS MY HOPE.

25:22.056 --> 25:23.391
THIS IS DESERT EAGLE.

25:23.424 --> 25:25.927
WE GOT MOJADOS
IN SECTOR FIVE.

25:25.960 --> 25:29.163
I REPEAT ‐‐
MOJADOS IN SECTOR FIVE.

25:29.197 --> 25:30.999
YOU GOT FIVE MINUTES

25:31.032 --> 25:34.102
BEFORE THE BORDER PATROL
GETS HERE, WILSON.

25:34.135 --> 25:36.371
I NEVER WANT TO SEE YOUR FACE
AGAIN.

25:37.739 --> 25:38.973
THANK YOU.

25:39.007 --> 25:40.341
THANK YOU.

25:40.375 --> 25:40.975
WAIT.

25:41.009 --> 25:42.944
GIVE ME ONE...

25:42.977 --> 25:44.712
JUST SO MY DAY'S NOT
A TOTAL LOSS.

25:44.746 --> 25:48.049
"GIVE YOU ONE"?
THESE ARE PEOPLE.

25:48.082 --> 25:49.484
LET'S JUST GIVE HIM THE GUY
WHO HUGGED ME.

25:49.517 --> 25:50.518
HE'S ANNOYING.

25:51.920 --> 25:54.122
YO, HOMBRE.
RáPIDO. LET'S GO.

25:54.155 --> 25:56.291
YOU, COME ON.
LET'S GO. OUT.

26:02.897 --> 26:04.699
NOW GET THE FUCK
OUT OF HERE.

26:04.732 --> 26:06.167
[ LAUGHS ]

26:06.201 --> 26:07.969
LET'S GO, ANDY, COME ON.

26:16.778 --> 26:18.346
Andy.
MM‐HMM?

26:18.379 --> 26:21.049
YOU WANT TO TAKE A WALK
OR SOMETHING?

26:21.082 --> 26:23.284
COME ON.
MM‐HMM.

26:23.318 --> 26:25.019
COME ON.

26:27.488 --> 26:29.357
SURE, WHY NOT?

26:34.162 --> 26:37.432
I'M A FUCKING LIAR.

26:37.465 --> 26:39.067
I WAS A BAD COYOTE.

26:39.100 --> 26:41.402
I LIE TO MYSELF
ALL THE TIME.

26:41.436 --> 26:43.271
I LET DOUG SACRIFICE
ONE OF MY PEOPLE.

26:43.304 --> 26:44.706
HE DID IT FOR LOVE,
BUT...

26:44.739 --> 26:47.408
I NEGOTIATE THINGS
THAT SHOULDN'T BE UP FOR DEBATE.

26:47.442 --> 26:50.111
I MAKE LITTLE COMPROMISES
WITH MYSELF.

26:50.144 --> 26:52.280
AND WHY DON'T I HAVE
A GIRLFRIEND?

26:52.313 --> 26:55.283
I TELL MYSELF I'M NOT DOING HARM
WHEN I AM.

26:55.316 --> 26:57.085
I SO AM!

26:57.118 --> 26:59.120
I WANT A GIRLFRIEND.

26:59.153 --> 27:01.322
I MEAN, I'M A GOOD GUY.

27:01.356 --> 27:03.124
I'M CUTE.

27:03.157 --> 27:06.027
AM I TOO OLD
FOR A GIRLFRIEND?

27:06.060 --> 27:08.563
NANCY, HAS MY WINDOW
OF OPPORTUNITY CLOSED?

27:08.596 --> 27:11.466
IS MY WINDOW SHUT, NANCE?

27:11.499 --> 27:13.735
HOW DID YOU OPEN
YOUR OWN WINDOW?

27:13.768 --> 27:14.702
DO YOU SEE HER?

27:14.736 --> 27:16.471
WHO?

27:16.504 --> 27:17.772
THERE.

27:17.805 --> 27:20.542
DO YOU SEE HER?

27:20.575 --> 27:23.311
SEE ‐‐ SEE ‐‐
SEE WHO?

27:23.344 --> 27:24.279
THERE!

27:26.581 --> 27:29.417
THERE'S NO ONE THERE.

27:32.353 --> 27:33.588
OH.

27:33.621 --> 27:35.256
RIGHT.

27:37.592 --> 27:39.627
OF COURSE NOT.
